{"tid":1811754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 武漢爆疫症 香港已累積14宗懷疑個案","createTime":"2020-01-05T03:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T05:44:37.000Z","uid":303740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06050554dce3159c00f7031a68b2ff10ddf9286f","tid":1811754,"uid":303740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢不明肺炎個案急增，而香港懷疑個案同步加劇。食衞局局長陳肇始出席公開場合時透露，截至今日，公立醫院於過去24小時接收多6名曾於過去14天到訪過武漢，並出現發燒、呼吸道感染或肺炎徵狀的病人，連同上述個案，公院自去年12月31日起，共向衞生署呈報14宗懷疑個案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200105&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60451969\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200105%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60451969&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=d0a184ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200105%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60451969&h=0bfb4a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200105&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60451969</a>"},{"pid":"dac9b93d75f43e35cff20d697fe3365b7e6197ca","tid":1811754,"uid":303740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"全民帶口罩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044ed437d833b0cbeeec2387c98c16b2898793ee","tid":1811754,"uid":303740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"條街仲係冇乜人帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係啲人唔知定仲覺得冇事"},{"pid":"3277567b387e0e0262f7e4f1dba02e2d0ed8b2a7","tid":1811754,"uid":15184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"搭車d人仲係唔戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d仆街咳又唔掩口又唔戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe427a163bb5795841bb6a2454ca25efa2d95be9","tid"